formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.	The compilation & certification of figures in the said RERA Form - 3 along-with applicable annexure are based & relied on 
-	Latest Architects & Engineers certificates regarding estimated construction cost, Nos. of Garage/covered/Open parking as per RERA, Calculation of carpet area of each & every units of the said project as per RERA & Percentage of completion of on-site works, 
-	Duly signed plan passed, 
-	Bank Statements up to 30-06-2022
-	Previous years Audited financials, 
-	Duly certified provisional financials up to 30-06-2022
-	Original signed Agreement to Sale up to 30-06-2022, 
which, and other information and explanation to the best of our knowledge and belief were necessary for the purpose of issuing this certificate.
2.	Amount deposited and withdrawn from the bank account reflects only booking receipts collected and utilized in the project.
3.	Management of the company has provided Customer ID, details of PAN and Mobile Numbers of the allottees and we have relied on the same and not given any certificate regarding the said information.   
4.	Above figures are certified based on positing in books of accounts as on 30-06-2022. Similarly detail in enclosed annexures are also as on 30-06-2022.
